      <div class="meth-h" style="font-size:12.5px;margin-top:1rem;border:none;color:var(--ink-2)">Method A — Multiplicative (default)<span class="derived-marker" title="Functional-form assumption: combining univariate ORs by multiplication assumes modifiers act independently on probability. This is a structural choice, not a literature finding. The logit-additive method (Method B) is an alternative structural choice. Neither has been validated against an ADP-specific multivariable regression.">†</span></div>
      <div class="meth-eq">
